  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and grated ginger, cooking for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced carrots, black pepper, smoked paprika, and namul-blanch-season, stirring to coat.",
    "Pour in the vegetable stock and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer until carrots are tender, about 20 minutes.",
    "Blend the soup with an immersion blender until smooth, then return to the pot.",
    "Stir in the muscovado sugar and salt, adjusting seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh dill."
  ],
